    "id": "200662070448291_1541615694640703",
    "message": "We've had a full year of harnessing the sun's energy to help power the brewery, and it's time to celebrate with a solar-powered beer!  \"Here Comes the Sun\" is a golden peachy lager grown by the sun and brewed with peaches from the farm on a sunny day with 100% solar power!  On tap today!  #peachesaresolarpoweredtoo #millionsofpeaches #reallyloveyourpeaches \n\nVisit Coshocton, Ohio! Ohio Craft Beer Northeast Ohio Craft Beverage News Paradise Energy Solutions \n@visitcoshocton @ohiocraftbeer @neo_craft_brewery_news @paradiseenergysolutions",
